23 SECTION 1. Arkansas Code Title 25, Chapter 1, is amended to add an
24 additional subchapter to read as follows:
25 Subchapter 13 — Arkansas Guidance Out of the Darkness Act
26
27 25-1-1301. Title.
28 This subchapter shall be known and cited as the "Arkansas Guidance Out
29 of the Darkness Act" or “Ark-GOOD Act".
30
31 25-1-1302. Legislative findings and intent.
32 (a) The General Assembly finds that:
33 (1) Transparency in government is essential to ensuring
34 accountability and maintaining public trust;
35 (2) Despite lacking the force of law, guidance from the United
36 States Government often:
